### 4. Lấy thông tin chi tiết CV (thay CV_ID bằng ID thực tế)
GET https://localhost:7217/api/cv/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### 5. Cập nhật CV
PUT https://localhost:7217/api/cv/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "CV Senior Frontend Developer",
  "isPublic": true,
  "isDefault": false
}

###

### 6. Xóa CV
DELETE https://localhost:7217/api/cv/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

